Item 2.02. Disclosure of Results of Operations.
 
The following information is being furnished under Item 12 of Form 8-K: News Release by The Boeing Company, for the first quarter results as announced on April 27, 2005. The text of the release is attached as exhibit 99.1 to this Form 8-K.
 
Item 9.01. Financial Statements and Exhibits
 
