On May 4, 2007, The Boeing Company (the "Company") announced that Richard D. Nanula resigned as a Director of the Company. Mr. Nanula was a member of the Audit, Finance and Special Programs Committees. Mr. Nanula has confirmed that his resignation was not due to a disagreement with the Company on any matter relating to the Company's operations, policies or practices. Mr. Nanula's resignation is effective immediately.
 
