Final Average Incentive Pay
However, if a Participant has commenced a benefit under this Plan following a deemed Separation from Service under Code section 409A due to an Authorized Period of Absence classified as Pre-Retirement Leave, awards made during this Authorized Period of Absence will not be included. Similarly, incentive awards will not be counted toward Final Average Incentive Pay to the extent awarded during a Participant's period of reduced services, where the Participant has Separated from Service due to a reasonably anticipated permanent reduction in services of at least 50 percent (for reasons other than an Authorized Period of Absence).
