On April 28, 2008, the Board of Directors amended and restated the By-Laws of The Boeing Company (the ""), revising Article II, Section 1 to decrease the number of directors from twelve to eleven. A copy of the Company's By-Laws, as amended and restated on April 28, 2008, is attached hereto as Exhibit 3.2 and is incorporated by reference.
