Item 2.02. Results of Operations and Financial Condition
(a) On July 22, 2009, The Boeing Company issued a press release reporting its financial results for the second quarter of 2009. A copy of the Company's press release is attached hereto as Exhibit 99.1 and is incorporated herein by reference.
