Two purported class actions have recently been filed in the United States District Courts in the Northern and Southern Districts of Illinois alleging, among other things, that The Boeing Company (the "") and certain officers made misleading statements regarding the status of the Company's 787 program. The Company believes that the lawsuits are without merit and will vigorously defend them.
