Item 2.02. Results of Operations and Financial Condition
(a) On October 20, 2010, The Boeing Company issued a press release reporting its financial results for the third quarter of 2010. A copy of the Company's press release is attached hereto as Exhibit 99.1 and is incorporated herein by reference.
Item 9.01. Financial Statements and Exhibits
(a) Not applicable
