Item 2.02. Results of Operations and Financial Condition
(a) On January 30, 2013, The Boeing Company issued a press release reporting its financial results for the fourth quarter of 2012. A copy of the Company's press release is furnished as Exhibit 99.1 to this Current Report on Form 8-K.
Item 9.01. Financial Statements and Exhibits
